text: Marechal Deodoro most commonly refers to: * Marechal Deodoro da Fonseca (1827–1892), President of Brazil It may also refer to: * Marechal Deodoro, Alagoas - a town in Brazil named after Deodoro da Fonseca * Marechal Deodoro (São Paulo Metro) == See also == * Deodoro (disambiguation)
title: Marechal Deodoro (disambiguation)
